{"word":"H454 - אֶלְיְהֹועֵינַי - ʼElyᵉhôwʻêynay - el-ye-ho-ay-nah'ee - Elihoenai","slug":"H454","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">אֶלְיְהֹועֵינַי</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʼElyᵉhôwʻêynay"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>el-ye-ho-ay-nah'ee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Elihoenai"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D0;&#x05DC;&#x05D9;&#x05D5;&#x05E2;&#x05D9;&#x05E0;&#x05D9;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05D0;&#x05DC;&#x05D9;&#x05D4;&#x05D5;&#x05E2;&#x05D9;&#x05E0;&#x05D9; - 'ely<sup>e</sup>ho&#x0302;&#x201B;e&#x0302;ynay  'elyo&#x0302;&#x201B;e&#x0302;ynay</b> - <i>el-ye-ho-ay-nah'ee, el-yo-ay-nah'ee</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H413\">H413</a> and <a href=\"#/H3068\">H3068</a> and <a href=\"#/H5869\">H5869</a>; <i>towards Jehovah</i> (are) <i>my eyes</i>; <i>Eljehoenai</i> or <i>Eljoenai</i>, the name of seven Israelites: - Elihoenai, Elionai."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H413\">H413</a>, <a href=\"#/H462\">H462</a>"}]}